      'hero.h1': 'Locksmith Oberpfalz<br />Door Opening &amp; Security in One Place',
      'hero.p1': 'When the door slams shut or the key breaks, every minute counts. Our regional team operates throughout the Oberpfalz and helps quickly, reliably and cleanly – whether for an apartment, house or commercial property.',
