      'services.card3.h3': 'On-Site Security Consultation',
      'services.card3.p': 'We analyse doors, windows and basement entrances and show how you can better protect your home – including installation of additional security fittings and armoured bolts.',
      'services.card4.h3': 'Window, Safe &amp; Garage Opening',
      'services.card4.p': 'In addition to front doors, we take care of window handles, garage doors or safes with mechanical locks. Tell us what needs opening – we bring the right tools.',
      'about.h2': 'Reliable, Regional &amp; Personal',
      'about.p1': 'For over ten years we have been the point of contact for door openings and security technology in the Oberpfalz. We see ourselves not as an anonymous emergency service, but as a regional craft firm that speaks with its customers at eye level. Every job is carried out by trained specialists.',
      'about.p2': 'Regular training, high-quality tools and extensive experience mean we can open almost any door without damage. If a lock does need replacing, we have the right spare parts directly in the vehicle.',
      'about.p3': 'Fair fixed prices are a matter of course for us. You will find out the costs by phone. On site we confirm the price in writing before we start work. This means you stay in control at all times.',
      'about.p4': 'In addition to emergency services, we advise on burglary prevention, plan locking systems for apartment buildings and support companies in securing their premises. Get in touch – we will find the right solution.',
      'areas.h2': 'Operating Throughout the Entire Oberpfalz',
      'areas.p': 'Our operations centre in Regensburg coordinates technicians in all districts of the Oberpfalz. This means we can reach you quickly – whether in the city or the countryside. Below you will find a selection of our most frequent deployment locations.',
      'emergency.h2': 'What to do in an Emergency?',
      'emergency.p': 'Stay calm – a brief phone call is all it takes and we will be on our way. To help you as efficiently as possible, we recommend the following steps:',
      'emergency.li1': '<strong>1. Check access:</strong> Take a look at balcony or patio doors. Perhaps there is another way into the house without calling us.',
      'emergency.li2': '<strong>2. Do not use force:</strong> Attempts with wire, cards or screwdrivers quickly cause expensive damage. Better to wait for our specialist tools.',
      'emergency.li3': '<strong>3. Call emergency number:</strong> Call us on <a href="tel:+4915153639881">0151 536 39881</a> and briefly describe the situation. We will immediately confirm the fixed price.',
      'emergency.li4': '<strong>4. Provide identification:</strong> Please have ID ready if possible. For your safety, we only open doors for authorised persons.',
      'emergency.highlight.h3.1': 'Transparent Prices &amp; Short Response Times',
      'emergency.highlight.p1': 'Day, night or weekend – we work with clear fixed prices. We communicate surcharges openly before costs arise. Travel, labour and materials are clearly itemised.',
      'emergency.highlight.h3.2': 'Workshop in the Vehicle',
      'emergency.highlight.p2': 'Our technicians carry the most common cylinder sizes, fittings and security products. This means we can take care of everything straight away – without a second appointment.',
      'emergency.cta1': 'Call immediately',
      'emergency.cta2': 'Send email',
