      'contact.map.hint': 'You can revoke your selection at any time via the cookie settings.',
      'reviews.h2': 'Voices from the Oberpfalz',
      'reviews.p': 'This is how customers rate our service after door openings, lock changes and consultations.',
      'reviews.1.quote': '"The door slammed shut with the key inside. 25 minutes after my call the technician arrived and opened the door without damage. Price as agreed in advance – highly recommended!"',
      'reviews.1.date': 'Review from 4 March 2025',
      'reviews.2.quote': '"Very friendly and competent. After a break-in attempt, the team installed a security cylinder the same evening and explained everything calmly. Many thanks!"',
      'reviews.2.date': 'Review from 18 February 2025',
      'region.h3': 'Oberpfalz in Focus',
      'region.h2.1': 'Roots in the Region – Local Help',
      'region.p1': 'Our locksmith service operates throughout the entire Oberpfalz. From Regensburg to Weiden, from Amberg to the Bavarian Forest – we know the routes, characteristics and people on the ground. This keeps travel times short and you receive help that is truly locally rooted.',
      'region.h2.2': 'Why a Local Partner is Beneficial',
      'region.p2': 'Regional presence means: no long waiting times, no travel from distant cities and a team that can assess the conditions of your town. We work transparently, document all work steps and give a clear assessment before costs arise.',
      'region.p3': 'Sensitivity is particularly required in old buildings and listed properties in the Oberpfalz. Our technicians bring experience with historical locks as well as modern locking systems in new builds or commercial properties.',
      'region.h2.3': 'More than Door Openings',
      'region.p4': 'In addition to classic door openings, we support you in planning additional security measures. These include reinforced strike plates, high-security cylinders or retrofitting complete locking systems. Together we find the right solution for your home or business.',
      'relatedlinks.h2': 'Further Information',
      'relatedlinks.p': 'Deepen your knowledge of security or find out about our services in other areas.',
      'relatedlinks.link1': 'Price Overview &amp; Services',
